---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Skief Labs" description="Terms of Service for Skief Labs Corp. Governing your engagement with our services.">
  <section class="bg-linen py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">

      <!-- Hero group -->
      <div class="reveal mb-12">
        <div class="inline-block border border-[#001d52] text-[#001d52] text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_#001d52] mb-6">Legal</div>
        <h1 class="heading-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.8rem] text-navy mb-4 leading-[1.1] uppercase">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-navy/50 text-sm">Last updated: March 6, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-navy max-w-none text-black text-base leading-relaxed">

        <!-- Intro -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <p>
            <strong class="text-black">Skief Labs Corp</strong><br />
            66 W Flagler Street, Suite 900, PMB 10451<br />
            Miami, FL 33130<br />
            <a href="mailto:contact@skieflabs.com" class="text-blue hover:text-blue">contact@skieflabs.com</a>
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4">These Terms of Service ("Terms") govern your engagement with Skief Labs Corp ("Skief Labs," "we," "us," or "our") and the services we provide. By signing a proposal or commencing a paid engagement with Skief Labs, you agree to these Terms.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>Skief Labs Corp is a Florida corporation (Document No. P19000059556) that designs and operates data intelligence and sales acceleration systems for B2B companies.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">2. Scope of Services</h2>
          <p>The specific services we provide are defined in a written proposal or statement of work ("Proposal") agreed to before work begins. We do not begin work before a Proposal is agreed and, where applicable, a deposit is received. Any changes to the agreed scope must be agreed in writing by both parties.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">3. Payment Terms</h2>
          <p>Fees are set out in the Proposal, in US dollars unless otherwise stated. Project-based engagements require a 50% deposit before work begins, with the remainder due on delivery. Monthly retainer engagements are invoiced at the start of each billing period and due within 14 days. Invoices not paid within 30 days may incur interest at 1.5% per month.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 4 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">4. Ownership & Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>Upon receipt of full payment, all systems, workflows, documentation, and deliverables created specifically for you become your property. We may use proprietary methods, frameworks, templates, and tooling which remain our property. Some systems rely on third-party platforms governed by their own terms. We design systems to be operated independently by your team.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 5 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">5. Confidentiality</h2>
          <p>Both parties agree to keep confidential any non-public information shared during the engagement. Confidentiality obligations survive termination for two (2) years.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 6 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">6. Data & Privacy</h2>
          <p>We use data you provide solely to deliver the agreed services. We do not sell, share, or repurpose your data.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 7 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">7. Representations & Warranties</h2>
          <p>Services will be performed with reasonable skill and care. We do not guarantee specific business outcomes including pipeline volume, revenue growth, data accuracy rates, or outbound reply rates.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 8 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Total liability shall not exceed the total fees paid in the three (3) months preceding the claim. Neither party shall be liable for indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 9 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">9. Termination</h2>
          <p>Either party may terminate with 30 days written notice. Upon termination: fees for completed work are due, all completed work product is delivered, confidentiality obligations remain.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 10 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">10. Independent Contractor</h2>
          <p>Skief Labs is an independent contractor. Nothing creates an employment, partnership, joint venture, or agency relationship.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 11 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
          <p>Governed by the laws of the State of Florida. Exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Miami-Dade County, Florida.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 12 -->
        <div class="reveal mb-6">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">12. General</h2>
          <p>These Terms and the applicable Proposal constitute the entire agreement. We may update these Terms from time to time.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 13 -->
        <div class="reveal">
          <h2 class="heading-serif text-xl text-navy !mt-12 !mb-4">13. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Skief Labs Corp<br />
            66 W Flagler Street, Suite 900, PMB 10451<br />
            Miami, FL 33130<br />
            <a href="mailto:contact@skieflabs.com" class="text-blue hover:text-blue">contact@skieflabs.com</a><br />
            <a href="https://skieflabs.com" class="text-blue hover:text-blue">https://skieflabs.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
